{"tid":2223802,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"啲廢老院七月害完我哋香港人而家又嚟過?","createTime":"2020-09-30T05:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T07:22:24.000Z","uid":237459,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4872d2843657ff7d651477b3c1208f1f4a39884","tid":2223802,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"消息指，本港今日新增約9宗新型肺炎確診個案，包括一名元朗護老院的女院友。據了解，她沒有發燒等病徵，化驗顯示對新型冠狀病毒有抗體。涉事的元朗護老院長者，昨晚已撤離。<br />\n<br />\n有業界指，由於相信再次出現安老院舍院友受感染，令原本打算在中秋期間作特別探訪的安排都立即叫停。<br />\n<br />\n有傳染病專家強調，現階段不是時候放寬院舍的探訪限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552415-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552415-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=b1e06148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552415-20200930.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=557a220d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552415-20200930.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8ca724ec0581db14bac695bf72b696f480059d77","tid":2223802,"uid":378177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:22:24.000Z","msg":"你好似掉轉咗黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該係香港人害老人院多啲bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係香港人將病毒帶入老人院，唔係老人院大病毒出社區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />住得老人院就唔會出去㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點會害到你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連登仔真係又自私又低能，抗爭加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}